name: The Splendor of Nudity Captured on Film V2

metadata.name: Passion dance
metadata.description:
She asked you to turn off the light and make yourself comfortable... After one long and languid moment of waiting she appeared in the doorway completely naked - just for you - and began her slow, smooth and hypnotizing movements.

She has rehearsed this in front of the mirror much more than once - and she knows for sure that you can hardly see anything other than her silhouette, but she perfectly sees your admiring look - do not take it away! She has just risen above all her complexes and doubts for your sake - and only your eyes allows her to stay above them.

***

Shot on medium format film camera
